{
  "stem": "4345.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened is we had a baker in our town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Gelsnaw, ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Schmeal ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Gelsnaw. ?] He owned a bakery, and we used to buy the breads there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had one son who was not so OK mentally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was-- he was a little bit retarded, you know, functioning but retarded.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he went into the bakery, and he turned on an oven.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Gestapo saw the smoke come out of the chimney.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they went into the bakery, and he saw that boy there, that young boy, you know, and they accused him of baking bread so that he could supply bread for the Jewish people of the town.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then, all of a sudden, we hear over the loudspeaker that the, [SPEAKING GERMAN], that the whole town is to get together, that they are going to-- we are going down to the [GERMAN]-- my friend's-- my friend's backyard, the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is where we are going to march down to this place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, you obey.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went like little sheep to the slaughter, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And before we reach the street, maybe a mile away, you could hear the music play.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know the music that they played was Mozart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mostly, it was the Mozart music that they played and laughter and singing and-- and-- and music was blasting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When we came close, there was a whole bash going on, a whole party the Nazis had, table full of food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were drinking, and they were going [NON-ENGLISH], nuts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, we see the gallows and seven nooses from the gallows, and of course, little boxes under each person to step on, you know, step on.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
